NetworkManager-vpn: NetworkManager (NetworkManager VPN Extensions)
NetworkManager-vpn:
NetworkManager-vpn: NetworkManager-vpn attempts to make networking invisible. When moving 
NetworkManager-vpn: into areas you've been before, NetworkManager-vpn automatically 
NetworkManager-vpn: connects to the last network the user chose to connect to. Likewise,
NetworkManager-vpn: when back at the desk, NetworkManager-vpn will switch to the faster,
NetworkManager-vpn: more reliable wired network connection. 
NetworkManager-vpn:
NetworkManager-vpn: This package provides NetworkManager with VPN Extensions for
NetworkManager-vpn: openvpn, vpnc and pptp.
NetworkManager-vpn:
